					<tr>
						<td colspan="4">Ok Shadows it's time to give MistMoor a payback!  This raid is for those 18+.  The zone line will be guarded by those of us who are 18-28.  Those of you who are higher get to venture deeper.  I have camped at the zone line a few times and it was awesome exp and good loot.  Healers are a must for each group and definitely need at least one tank per group.  So get your maps ready.  Go to www.eqatlas.com to get your copy.  There are a lot of quest items related to this place so take a look at www.alakhazams.com to find out if anything there is of interest to you.  Hope to see a good turnout.</td>
